title: Rito hat mir Soulstealer Vayne zu Weihnachten geschenkt :)

embed.description: Hello guys, i've bought 10 winter chests today on 24th december for the event summoner icon and ingame emote. I opened the 10 and couldnt believe my eyes!! I got soulstealer vayne + 2 additional gemstones (which are not in this video file). How can one be that lucky? Merry christmas!
